{"tid":2003634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"校監丁媽去年回理大設社工站安撫同學情緒翌日被捕：「好似阿媽坐喺仔女房門口，陪住緊張不安嘅仔女咁，有乜事我擋先。」","createTime":"2020-05-06T03:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T03:41:26.000Z","uid":125168,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"518d23ffbb74f5bd806c8044a8c35f910d6581f2","tid":2003634,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:06:36.000Z","msg":"全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200506/Y6OPNLHNGFK6JWIIL4RHIM2B5Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200506%2FY6OPNLHNGFK6JWIIL4RHIM2B5Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=5dcd67e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200506%2FY6OPNLHNGFK6JWIIL4RHIM2B5Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=341faf4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200506/Y6OPNLHNGFK6JWIIL4RHIM2B5Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n該「家長聯會」成員甚至進行起底式批鬥，指太陽島英文幼稚園校監丁惠芳是「黃絲暴徒」、「毒害青年」。家長聯會又涉起底，指丁惠芳是前理大應用社會科學系副教授。<br />\n<br />\n去年11月11日，同學退守理大，已退休的丁媽亦回校設社工站，安撫同學情緒。11月17日，理大被困，翌日早上丁媽被捕。她受訪時憶述，留守理大的學生最怕警察突然衝入，她就一直坐在走廊，守着房裏的學生，「好似阿媽坐喺仔女房門口，陪住緊張不安嘅仔女咁，有乜事我擋先。」"},{"pid":"1651696416ab7eaf413cf9d3b03d237a208a6fbd","tid":2003634,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:06:53.000Z","msg":"d 藍屍自己對號入座<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去學校到繼續幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2248786422026053/posts/2568242556747103/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2248786422026053%2Fposts%2F2568242556747103%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=8fc0a34d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2248786422026053/posts/2568242556747103/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n幫拖！太陽島幼稚園被藍屍五毛攻擊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2002289\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2002289</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"78fdaa2b9085ed4ae29eee9b212b68030f38f88d","tid":2003634,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"睇親呢d新聞就覺得分化撚零舍低賤，以前一遊行完就幾多牛鬼蛇神岀嚟屌和理非好廢好無用"},{"pid":"302f186563524305be025b747abc05f17fe0da89","tid":2003634,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:11:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"626fff16424bace23bedc2efbfe890200829905a","tid":2003634,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f85e941dc4ee9fb5639e8e489e8459e96948ed9","tid":2003634,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:18:28.000Z","msg":"咁警犬應該叫乜好?<br />\n<br />\n根本自己對號入座，疑心生暗鬼"},{"pid":"577a1f8db4ba8235a29c89a4a01b37a11465b516","tid":2003634,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T03:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}